If its HIGHLIGHT slot is nil, then don't highlight it."
  (let ((section (magit-current-section))
        (refinep (lambda ()
                   (and magit-highlighted-section
                        (eq magit-diff-refine-hunk t)
                        (eq (magit-section-type magit-highlighted-section)
